I have a question:

Has the Harvard Dataverse server been running the "UVA_Authored_Datasets" set? Should I contact "Support" at Harvard?

On Harvard Dataverse - searching authorAffiliation:"University of Virginia" gives me 194 datasets, but I only have 183 in our local repo and running the harvesting client does't give me any new ones.

Should I create a new client? UVA is at V6.2
Yeah, this is a good question for support@dataverse.harvard.edu since it's specific to Harvard Dataverse.
